doc.title: barnaamijyada
doc.description: Qaybtani waxa ay ku saabsan tahay sida barnaamijka loo sameeyo

example1.title: {{0}}Tusaale summada bogga guriga
example1.annotation1: Go'aanso in uu yahay isla magaca domainka hoose haddii kale, soo celi {{0}} oo mar dambe ha fulin.
example1.annotation2: Go'aanso inay tahay {{0}} ama bogga hoyga kanaalka jidkiisu wuxuu ka bilaabmaa @ sumadda, ku celi {{1}}
example1.annotation3: Go'aanso in uu yahay bog muuqaal ah.
example1.annotation4: Go'aanso in ay tahay bog fiidyow oo gaaban.
example1.annotation5: Xaalado kale, {{0}} waa la soo celiyay.
